	    <module name="StaticContentSample" layoutPanel="panel_row1_col1">
      <param name="text">
	This dashboard provides Windows PerfMon information regarding Network utilization across your virtual desktops. VMs in the High Throughput table are VMs whose Throughput  is above a defined threshold. You can filter this view by entering values in the fields below and pressing enter. Selecting a hostname from the table will take you to a detailed Network utilization report for that desktop. For detailed views on other counters look under Reports/Environment in the navigation above.
	To view the entire result set for this report or manipulate the data further, click View Full Report.

</param>
    </module>

